---
/**
 * DistributorHeroStitch.astro
 * Hero section for the Become a Distributor page.
 */
---

<header class="relative pt-36 pb-28 px-6 overflow-hidden bg-[#200f01]">

  <!-- Ambient blobs -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-25 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-[32rem] h-[32rem] bg-[#ffd700] rounded-full blur-[150px] animate-pulse"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-[28rem] h-[28rem] bg-[#ce0301] rounded-full blur-[150px] animate-pulse" style="animation-delay:-2s;"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10 text-center space-y-6">
    <div class="inline-block bg-[#ce0301] text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-full font-headline font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-sm -rotate-2 shadow-lg">
      Partner With Us
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-headline font-black text-[#ffd700] leading-none tracking-tighter uppercase">
      Become a<br />
      <span class="text-[#f2cdff] italic">Distributor</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium max-w-2xl mx-auto text-[#d0c6ab] leading-tight opacity-90">
      Grow with Coco Cado and bring an exciting snack brand to your market. Let's make every bite a celebration.
    </p>

    <div class="flex justify-center gap-3 pt-2" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="h-2 w-20 bg-[#ce0301] rounded-full"></div>
      <div class="h-2 w-10 bg-[#ffd700] rounded-full"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Wavy divider — colour matches next section bg -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-[-2px] left-0 w-full h-24 bg-[#2a1705] wavy-divider-top z-10" aria-hidden="true"></div>
</header>
